                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-00">
                    Phone Support
                  </h3>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-base text-text-00">
                    Call us for immediate assistance or to schedule an
                    appointment.
                  </p>
                  <a
                    href="tel:01273123456"
                    class="mt-2 inline-block rounded-md px-1 font-semibold text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:outline-none"
                  >
                    01273 123 456
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start gap-x-4">
                <div class="flex-none">
                  <div
                    class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent-500"
                  >
                    <svg
                      class="h-6 w-6 text-background-00"
                      fill="none"
                      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                      stroke-width="1.5"
                      stroke="currentColor"
                      aria-hidden="true"
                    >
                      <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 19.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07-1.916V6.75"
                      ></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-00">
                    Get a Quote
                  </h3>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-base text-text-00">
                    Request a free, no-obligation quote for your project.
                  </p>
                  <a
